description.en:
Bebop-Inu was founded by a team of crypto and anime enthusiasts. The name was inspired by crypto’s most-loved dog, the Shiba Inu, as well as one of anime’s most famous shows - Cowboy Bebop.

Like the characters in Cowboy Bebop, the Bebop-Inu cryptocurrency is all about living in
the future. $Bebop-Inu will be the spaceship that helps our community to achieve financial freedom, and be a part of a truly innovative mission.
